dct_title_s: Map of the country between Bhamo and Momein shewing the route of the expedition under the command of Major E. B. Sladen
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Includes inset map of a sketch map of Irrawaddy River from mouths of the Irrawaddy to Bhamo. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 41 (1871), pp.257-81; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1872.
